Notes:


    Responsiveness
        
        Fluidity
        
            Use percentages
        
            Use flexbox

        Elasticity

            REMS
                Looks at the html root element:

                   html{ font-size: 10px; }
                
                   .someClass{ font-size: 1rem; }

            EMS
                Closest parent font size:

                    <div class="someClass">
                        <p class="subClass"></p>
                    </div>

                    .someClass{ font-size: 10px; }

                    .subClass{ font-size: 2em; }

    

